OL,3,CCorrie star demonstrates how he copes
OL,4,Cwith essential tremor on set
OL,6,FRob Mallard spoke to Granada Reports
OL,7,Fentertainment correspondent Caroline
OL,8,FWhitmore about his role as patron for
OL,9,Fyoung people at the Tremor Foundation.
OL,11,FRob Mallard is a familiar face in The
OL,12,FRovers Return, the actor has played
OL,13,FDaniel Osbourne on Coronation Street
OL,14,Fsince 2015.
OL,16,FHe has spoken out about the condition
OL,17,Fessential tremor after he was
OL,18,Fdiagnosed at the age of 14, but says
OL,19,Fhis symptoms are slowly getting worse.
