OL,3,CCorrie star demonstrates how he copes
OL,4,Cwith essential tremor on set
OL,6,FEssential tremor is a common
OL,7,Fneurological disorder that causes an
OL,8,Funcontrollable shake or trembling in a
OL,9,Fpart of the body.
OL,11,FRob says "When I was diagnosed it was
OL,12,Fjust my left hand, now it is both
OL,13,Fhands and I will get it in the
OL,14,Fdiaphragm and I have had the head
OL,15,Ftremor in the past"
OL,17,F"It was something I didn't want to
OL,18,Ftalk about, I just wanted to hide it,
OL,19,Fbut I can't now because it is obvious."
