OL,3,CCorrie star demonstrates how he copes
OL,4,Cwith essential tremor on set
OL,6,FThe 29-year-old, who is from Oldham,
OL,7,Fis now using his time in the spotlight
OL,8,Fto educate others about the condition.
OL,10,F"A lot of people assume it is an
OL,11,Fanxiety disorder, even worse than that
OL,12,Fthey can assume you are in withdrawal
OL,13,Ffrom having a drink"
OL,15,FThe actor showed how the tremor
OL,16,Fbecomes obvious when he picks up a
OL,17,Fglass
