OL,3,CCorrie star demonstrates how he copes
OL,4,Cwith essential tremor on set
OL,6,FRob has taken on the role as patron
OL,7,Ffor young people at the Tremor
OL,8,FFoundation and wants to help improve
OL,9,Feducation about the condition and help
OL,10,Fpeople talk about it.
OL,12,FMore than a million people live with
OL,13,Fthe condition in the UK which is
OL,14,Festimated to be eight to 10 times more
OL,15,Fcommon than Parkinson's disease.
